::Feline::

She smiled at him.  "Since you were shown the bridge and given access 
to all computers, we can cause a great amount of chaos." she purred 
and smiled at the thought.  "I have been instructed to help the bots 
that are damaged and repair them. I can do many things, install a 
program that would put that bot under our control for instance."
She purred softly as she walked.  She liked the ideas brewing in her 
mind. "But i would have to wait for a little while.  This 
bot..ah..Dinobot and the other, Travatron.  I think I can make this 
situation very useful to us." She had been speaking in a hushed tone 
so no other bots could over hear.  She smiled at the possabilities.
